  {
   "question": "What is the Season 4 arena set for Destruction Warlock?",
   "answer": "The Brutal Gladiator's pieces: Brutal Gladiator's Dreadweave Leggings, Brutal Gladiator's Spellblade, Brutal Gladiator's Touch of Defeat. The 2-piece and 4-piece set bonuses carry over between seasons, so partial upgrades never break your bonus."
