  {
   "question": "What are the rating requirements in Season 4?",
   "answer": "Season 4 has the strictest gates in TBC: the Brutal weapon requires 1950 rating, shoulders 2200, and several pieces check personal rating as well as team rating."
  },
  {
   "question": "How many arena points does full Season 4 gear cost?",
   "answer": "The five set pieces total roughly 8,250 arena points (helm/chest/legs 1,875 each, shoulders 1,500, gloves 1,125) plus about 3,750 for a main weapon. Use the arena points calculator to turn your weekly rating into a purchase timeline."
  },
  {
   "question": "Which honor pieces complement the Season 4 set?",
